**Title:** Whispering Waves and Starlit Dreams

**Description:** Drift into a peaceful slumber with Finn, a spirited thirteen-year-old boy, and his playful otter companion, Ripple, as they wander along the tranquil coastal shoreline. As the sun sets, casting golden hues over the sands, Finn embarks on a journey of resilience, facing gentle challenges with the guidance of nature's serene beauty. This calming tale invites you to breathe deeply, releasing anxiety and fostering emotional calm through the soothing sounds of the ocean and the tender companionship of an ever-watchful otter. Immerse yourself in the rhythmic lullaby of the waves and let the stars above cradle you into a restful night's sleep.

